"title": "5270: court",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5270",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Usually, a legal body dispensing justice, but the word may also refer to a royal court, the original function of which was the dispensation of justice by the monarch.</p>\n<h2>Courts of law</h2>\n<h3>Provision for and procedures of courts</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod18:25-Exod18:26\">EXO 18:25–18:26</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut1:15-Deut1:17\">DEU 1:15–1:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut17:9\">DEU 17:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth4:2-Ruth4:5\">RUT 4:2–4:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr26:29\">1CH 26:29</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr19:8-2Chr19:11\">2CH 19:8–19:11</a></p>\n<h3>Justice dispensed by the court</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut25:1\">DEU 25:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job11:10\">JOB 11:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos5:15\">AMO 5:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech8:16-Zech8:17\">ZEC 8:16–8:17</a></p>\n<h3>Disputes settled in court</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg4:4-Judg4:5\">JDG 4:4–4:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod21:22\">EXO 21:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job5:4\">JOB 5:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job9:32-Job9:35\">JOB 9:32–9:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov25:7-Prov25:8\">PRO 25:7–25:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov29:9\">PRO 29:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:25-Matt5:26\">MAT 5:25–5:26</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:58-Luke12:59\">LUK 12:58–12:59</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts18:12-Acts18:17\">ACT 18:12–18:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts19:38-Acts19:39\">ACT 19:38–19:39</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts25:1-Acts26:27\">ACT 25:1–26:27</a></p>\n<h3>Provision for a court of appeal</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut17:8-Deut17:13\">DEU 17:8–17:13</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Corruption in the court</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov22:22-Prov22:23\">PRO 22:22–22:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod23:1-Exod23:3\">EXO 23:1–23:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod23:6-Exod23:8\">EXO 23:6–23:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job31:21-Job31:22\">JOB 31:21–31:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa29:20-Isa29:21\">ISA 29:20–29:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos5:7-Amos5:15\">AMO 5:7–5:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas2:6\">JAS 2:6</a></p>\n<h3>The divine lawcourt</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan7:9-Dan7:10\">DAN 7:9–7:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa3:13-Isa3:17\">ISA 3:13–3:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan7:23-Dan7:27\">DAN 7:23–7:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor4:2-1Cor4:5\">1CO 4:2–4:5</a></p>\n<h2>Royal courts</h2>\n<h3>Egyptian</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen50:4-Gen50:7\">GEN 50:4–50:7</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Israelite</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer29:2\">JER 29:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs3:15\">1KI 3:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer34:19-Jer34:20\">JER 34:19–34:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer41:16\">JER 41:16</a></p>\n<h3>Babylonian</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:48-Dan2:49\">DAN 2:48–2:49</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan1:3-Dan1:5\">DAN 1:3–1:5</a></p>\n<h3>Persian</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth4:11\">EST 4:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth5:1-Esth5:2\">EST 5:1–5:2</a></p>\n<h3>The divine courts</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps84:10\">PSA 84:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps65:4\">PSA 65:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps84:1-Ps84:2\">PSA 84:1–84:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps92:12-Ps92:13\">PSA 92:12–92:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps96:8\">PSA 96:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps100:4\">PSA 100:4</a></p>",
